Package com.weather.sdk

Class SDKMetrics

java.lang.Object
com.weather.sdk.SDKMetrics
public final class SDKMetrics extends Object
Immutable snapshot of SDK performance metrics and statistics.

This class provides operational metrics including:

  • Total API requests made
  • Cache hit/miss statistics
  • API success/failure rates
  • Average response times
  • Last API call timestamp

Thread Safety: This class is immutable and thread-safe. Instances represent a point-in-time snapshot and will not be updated.

Since:
1.0.0

      public SDKMetrics(long totalRequests, long successCount, long failedRequests, long cacheHits, long cacheMisses, double avgResponseMs, Instant lastApiCallTime)
      Creates a new SDKMetrics instance with the specified values.
      Parameters:
      totalRequests - total number of API requests made
      successCount - number of successful API requests
      failedRequests - number of failed API requests
      cacheHits - number of cache hits
      cacheMisses - number of cache misses
      avgResponseMs - average response time in milliseconds
      lastApiCallTime - timestamp of the last API call, may be null
